songs.title: SOTG Remix Intro
songs.lyrics:
[Tech N9ne:Intro]
Yo whats up I'm sorry y'all I have to break up the album real quick man
But I have to share this with my fans
I think its the shit ummm this right here is
Straight out the gate but its the Scott Stevens Remix
Featuring John 5 man I had to share it with you
Cause I loved the song straight out the gate
And Scott Stevens did the remix and put John 5 on it man
And uhh whats up Serj Tankian lets do this man
Straight out the gate and then we'll get back to the album lets go. Tech N9ne
